des:
Princeton Scoop is your guide to the beautiful town of Princeton, New Jersey. With this skill visitors can find places to eat, places to shop or find things to do.
After you enable this skill, simply ask Alexa “Open Princeton Scoop” and she will offer you options to navigate your day and plan your time in Princeton, New Jersey.
You can get specific, for instance if you are looking to have lunch with the kids or an adult-only dinner, shop for your home or yourself, or attend a cultural or sporting event. There are lots of great choices and reasons to Princeton Scoop. Come explore the town with us.
Developed by PrincetonScoop, town’s cultural attache, you can access tons more information about the goings on in Princeton here
